    ParticleEffect Library v1.2 This library was created by @DarkBlade12 based on content related to particles of @microgeek (names and packet values) and allows you to display all Minecraft particle effects on a Bukkit server a You are welcome to use it, modify it and redistribute it under the following conditions: 1. Credit us if you publish a plugin that uses this library 2. Don't remove this text
